Package nusri.fyp.demo.roboflow.data.request

Class WorkflowSpecificationInferenceRequest

java.lang.Object
nusri.fyp.demo.roboflow.data.RoboflowRequestData
nusri.fyp.demo.roboflow.data.request.WorkflowSpecificationInferenceRequest
public class WorkflowSpecificationInferenceRequest extends RoboflowRequestData
Represents a request for workflow specification inference.
This request is used to trigger an inference process using a specified workflow. It includes various inputs and specification details necessary for the inference process.
